  "detailed_description": "<h1>About us</h1><p>Youtube：@TheFightOfEscaper</p><br><h1>DISCORD COMMUNITY</h1><p>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About the Game</h2></strong><br>You are a product of artificial intelligence created to take part in an experiment on \"self-awareness\". In your bid to escape, you arrive at the ends of the world. Right when you think you have evaded capture and escaped the clutches of AI, you discover that everything you have been through is all just a lie.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1097050/extras/87a3d80194746b42711d6d2d6681384c.poster.avif?t=1727058684\" width=750 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1097050/extras/87a3d80194746b42711d6d2d6681384c.webm?t=1727058684\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1097050/extras/87a3d80194746b42711d6d2d6681384c.mp4?t=1727058684\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>\"The Fight of Escaper\" is a Roguelike shooter game with cyberpunk aesthetics. You can choose from 1 male character and 2 female characters whose bodies and weapons have been cybernetically enhanced. They possess combat skills and abilities superior to those of robots.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1097050/extras/453cff38b9b1c90bc0294b73abe9da68.poster.avif?t=1727058684\" width=750 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1097050/extras/453cff38b9b1c90bc0294b73abe9da68.webm?t=1727058684\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1097050/extras/453cff38b9b1c90bc0294b73abe9da68.mp4?t=1727058684\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In the cyber world, there are hundreds of plugin items that can be used to enhance AI. These items are not just combat weapons, they are also essential in developing unique, personalized combat tactics. Strategically choosing the right combo of items to enhance your body will enable you to surpass and dominate AI in combat.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1097050/extras/5a8c66845dfda8877a78ee0d4a38c67d.poster.avif?t=1727058684\" width=750 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1097050/extras/5a8c66845dfda8877a78ee0d4a38c67d.webm?t=1727058684\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1097050/extras/5a8c66845dfda8877a78ee0d4a38c67d.mp4?t=1727058684\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In addition to these plugin items, there is vast potential for body customization. Combining various weapons, module abilities, talents, databases and outfits will allow for a thrilling combat experience.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【Game Features】</strong></h2><br>★★★A huge variety of cyberpunk-style maps and scenes create an immersive gameplay experience.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1097050/extras/df90ebfd91c1bcb6c2a5542fc981aa35.poster.avif?t=1727058684\" width=750 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1097050/extras/df90ebfd91c1bcb6c2a5542fc981aa35.webm?t=1727058684\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1097050/extras/df90ebfd91c1bcb6c2a5542fc981aa35.mp4?t=1727058684\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>★★★Equip your protagonist with exclusive skills and stylish outfits, expanding the variety of options for both solo and team combat.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1097050/extras/d5bb9bb2edb53cf964e53360ae7a7eea.poster.avif?t=1727058684\" width=750 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1097050/extras/d5bb9bb2edb53cf964e53360ae7a7eea.webm?t=1727058684\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1097050/extras/d5bb9bb2edb53cf964e53360ae7a7eea.mp4?t=1727058684\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>★★★Experience the thrill of growth as you try out different builds with each death and revival that you go through.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1097050/extras/247dcb4b02cc555db058057aa07082a2.poster.avif?t=1727058684\" width=750 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1097050/extras/247dcb4b02cc555db058057aa07082a2.webm?t=1727058684\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1097050/extras/247dcb4b02cc555db058057aa07082a2.mp4?t=1727058684\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>★★★The combination of hardcore mecha bosses and manic shooter mechanics makes for a challenging yet rewarding combat experience.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1097050/extras/f76982cdff939fba8cbd082fa9fe7001.poster.avif?t=1727058684\" width=750 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1097050/extras/f76982cdff939fba8cbd082fa9fe7001.webm?t=1727058684\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https: